# Competition Page Structure

This rule defines the standard structure for competition information pages (e.g., `app/competitions/[competition-name]/page.tsx`). These pages are intended for competitors and contain detailed information organized in an accordion format.

## File Structure

For a new competition, create a folder in `app/competitions/[competition-name]/` with two files:

1.  `layout.tsx`: Define metadata and hide from search engines.
2.  `page.tsx`: The main content page.

## Template: layout.tsx

```tsx
import type { Metadata } from "next";

export const metadata: Metadata = {
  title: "Competidores - [Competition Name]",
  robots: {
    index: false,
    follow: false,
  },
};

export default function CompetitionLayout({
  children,
}: {
  children: React.ReactNode;
}) {
  return children;
}
```

